00:36:24,066 --> 00:36:25,699
Right? I'm sorry!

762
00:36:25,735 --> 00:36:28,652
No, God, I'm over it, OK? You came back!

763
00:36:28,704 --> 00:36:30,905
You came back and now you're here,

