766
00:36:35,878 --> 00:36:38,913
Then what are you...
What do you mean, "the chosen"?

767
00:36:40,333 --> 00:36:43,634
- Wav, just say it, say it.
- I should be the heir!

768
00:36:44,754 --> 00:36:46,387
Yeah, you should.

769
00:36:47,590 --> 00:36:49,807
- I'm sorry.
- I forgive you.

