00:41:09,147 --> 00:41:12,231
A bona-fide miracle. I am cured!

851
00:41:14,903 --> 00:41:17,820
How, Doc? How did you do this?

852
00:41:17,856 --> 00:41:20,239
♪ I see the black You see the moon ♪

853
00:41:20,275 --> 00:41:22,775
Sweet mercy.

