867
00:41:53,308 --> 00:41:56,309
But what you have done pains me more.

868
00:41:58,446 --> 00:42:00,863
It's still me, Wyatt.

869
00:42:00,899 --> 00:42:02,949
Your friend, your brother!

870
00:42:02,984 --> 00:42:05,952
Doc Holliday is dead.

